title: Wholesale Price of Print Cloth, Mills for United States
notes:
Series Has Been Subdivided Into Four Variables: (1)-- Original Data, 1890-1913; (2)--Original Data, 1914-1943; (3)-- Original Data, 1943-1946; (4)--Original Data, 1946-1958. Data Refers To Print Cloth, 28", 64X64 And Are The Monthly Averages Of Weekly Prices. Data From 1890-1901 Were Computed By NBER. Source: Bls Bulletin No. 39, Pp. 364-365, And Following Issues

This NBER data series m04086a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 4 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter04.html.
